Class LinkSnapshot

java.lang.Object
  sailpoint.object.LinkSnapshot
All Implemented Interfaces:

NativeChangeDetection
public class LinkSnapshot
extends java.lang.Object
implements LinkInterface, java.io.Serializable

An object which represents a definition of a Link a given point in time.

This object is serialized as xml and is a private object of IdentitySnapshot object.
